data.description: The most fun opportunity paired with a fabulous home at the end of secluded cul de sac you'll find! Decor, segways, scooters, go carts, arcade games, 16 tv's & more will stay! 3 en suites, 1 on each level + 5 full baths - choose your level - each one also has a family room, study or office for your own private space. Built ins on 1 wall, a wall of windows with automatic blinds in spacious living room open to kitchen with perfect working space & breakfast area leading out to screened porch with gas fireplace - does casually elegant entertaining get any easier? Family room at the top of the steps, 2 bedrooms, full bath, 2nd laundry room & so charming, large bonus room made into a media area & bedroom. Downstairs is where it's all happening! Incredible wet bar will make you feel like you've just walked into a downtown bar! Waterfall edge bar, special lighting, dishwasher, mini fridge gives guests a relaxing spot to relax & watch the others playing pool, vintage arcade games & new video games - yes, they all stay along with all the neon lights! Office is equally impressive & you can cancel your membership at the gym - the gym equipment is all yours as well!
